column5: Haven't seen any reports from Eddie North, lately! Sure could use the information.
Nice post, and glad to see you changed your handle Mushmouth
Just wait til May. It is an awesome place. Go there and you will see.
I have to admit, Eddie North is on my Canadian Bucket list. Just not in '12
I'm penciled in for September, not sure how many guys yet, might be looking for anyone interested. I'll be talking to him this winter.

Well it seems the "natives" must be getting restless to bring up Eddie North again! Things to slow down and get a little boring, some stirring the pot will help us pass the time until next season opens!
